title: Girls volleyball: Victories for Maine West, Christian Liberty
text: Daily Herald report Maine West's girls volleyball team defeated Highland Park 22-25, 25-17, 25-22 on Wednesday night in Des Plaines. Seniors Allison Grzebien, Jordan Hart, Carly Hart and Hannah Kuhn led the way for the Warriors (9-19) who improved their record to 4-4 in the Central Suburban North. CLA d. Faith Lutheran: Christian Liberty posted a 25-16, 25-21 victory as Emily Naubert (9 kills) and Lexi Lee (7 kills) helped lead the way. Share this page
